{"tid":2132674,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"健康劈佛+撚廚.....減肥餐","createTime":"2020-07-30T13:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T15:41:12.000Z","uid":228002,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5efa20ac1ef8b19296890be70cd54b1afeab2580","tid":2132674,"uid":228002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"本身諗住今朝鋪po<br />\n點知數據爆咗upload唔到啲相上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MTbSqQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMTbSqQF.png&h=a1365fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日第一次試連皮食嘅奇異果<br />\n我想講真係好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKxqLQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKxqLQP.png&h=488a8440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香草雞胸肉50g<br />\n+菠菜 150g<br />\n+雞蛋1隻<br />\n+金奇異果2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撚廚減肥餐 <br />\n我今次係整得有啲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墨西哥卷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yw0TajW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyw0TajW.png&h=df588c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青瓜 60g<br />\n青椒 33g<br />\n牛油果 45g<br />\n紅蘿蔔 85g<br />\n炒蘑菇 37.5g<br />\n黑蒜頭 2粒<br />\n香草雞胸肉 150g<br />\n雞蛋 1隻<br />\n是啦差 5g<br />\n黃芥末 5g<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSQf76N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSQf76N.png&h=63ce2a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4juD5TB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4juD5TB.png&h=be51cb0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8d5a14d23e1219dcfb822b93c937bc35288eb0f","tid":2132674,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},{"pid":"7c23f629c5e26aa29cd3cc1f6a6911c62191ad5f","tid":2132674,"uid":146515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"咁似subway 幾勁"},{"pid":"cddef282a1b74e76b1ec1cde426bcdd350c1f856","tid":2132674,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"個卷好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bbd4b8b3a63029cc495a7e7f37cc13d482ed90","tid":2132674,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"連皮食感覺如何？<br />\n想試下 但係唔知會唔會有毛毛嘅奇怪感覺"},{"pid":"2fb18f3f1c23d501551ed916acae3d0bcd87be05","tid":2132674,"uid":310712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:44:46.000Z","msg":"個卷好似好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da37a7ea182e9a87523f43c8cc2029ef0bc1a5","tid":2132674,"uid":228002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d5a14d23e1219dcfb822b93c937bc35288eb0f","tid":2132674,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8611fa02ce5ae85eacd8dd95692df6e58dfd6d","tid":2132674,"uid":228002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cddef282a1b74e76b1ec1cde426bcdd350c1f856","tid":2132674,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"個卷好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=